wr-hac-agent layer
==================

This is a layer to add connectivity to the Wind River Helix App
Cloud. This includes:

* The  necessary kernel components and files in the target file  
  system (feature/hac). This feature is required.

* The necessary scripts to add target based registration from
  the command line (feature/omdlineregister).  This feature
  is optonal.

* The necessary scripts to add target based registration using
  a target based web server (feature/webregister). This 
  feature is optional.  If used, feature/cmdlineregister is 
  required. 

To use the layer, include it in a --with-layer option to configure.
In addition, add the desired features with --with-template 
option to configure.

